          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontsize='11'>Are separate from scorecard indices in the Community Living, Community Participation, Work Economic categories. Rather, they are an aggregation of the 100pt scores for each measure within a category. This allows us to see how a state is doing on a 100pt scale for a category such as Community Living, overall.</run>
